</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nc">.il</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="na">color</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="mh">#009999</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nc">.gc</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="na">color</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="mh">#999</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="na">background-color</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="mh">#EAF2F5</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nt">div</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nc">.gd</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">.gd</span> <span class="nc">.x</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">.gi</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">.gi</span> <span class="nc">.x</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="na">display</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="no">inline</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="no">block</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="na">width</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="p">}}</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure> </p>

<p>To get the highlighted text to appear to be actually highlighted within the
<code>include_code</code> blocks with the Github syntax highlighting applied, I also updated
